{"tid":1712960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大學生今晚用性命保護的不止是中大，而是全香港","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T16:02:15.000Z","uid":278052,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b39fef9928917fc78e104aeec7bd0b32b83732c7","tid":1712960,"uid":278052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔攻城大？唔攻港大？又唔攻科大？<br />\n<br />\n<ins>中大碧秋樓擁香港所有對外網絡控制權<br />\n而且有香港國際互聯網交換中心<br />\n係香港以至亞洲地區最重要既網絡資訊樞紐<br />\n如果比黑警攻左入去<br />\n全面控制網絡，中斷對外聯繫易如反掌</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在此謹感謝中大學生今晚展示出無比堅毅與勇氣<br />\n祈求受傷眾人早日康復<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n原文自fb page：Business Digest<br />\n<br />\n【#商業冷知識】你知道中文大學碧秋樓被校方稱為「香港網絡要塞」嗎？<br />\n<br />\n根據香港中文大學校友事務處（CUHK Alumni Affairs Office）形容，中大碧秋樓是「香港網絡要塞」，擔當極重要地位。文末連結已提供source作Fact Check。<br />\n<br />\n碧秋樓本為一所綜合大樓，後慢慢發展為資訊科技服務處(Information Technology Services Centre，簡稱ITSC)的基地。<br />\n<br />\n自90年代開始，ITSC於大樓內設立「香港國際網際網路交換中心」(Hong Kong Internet Exchange, HKIX)，令碧秋樓逐漸發展成為香港網際網路的中樞。HKIX的設立使香港區內的互聯網訊息交換直接傳輸而無需要繞經海外，從而節省時間和成本。現時，超過200家網路服務供應商、網絡機構以至大型網站，例如Google香港、Facebook、雅虎及微軟等均與HKIX連線。<br />\n<br />\n另外，根據香港中文大學及HKIX發表的報告，逾99%香港境內的互聯網訊息交換在此直接交换傳輸而無需要繞經海外，從而節省時間和成本。根據HKIX的官方簡介，HKIX為所有本地和國際網絡提供服務，包括商業服務提供商以及研究和教育網絡。由於其規模大和服務量大，HKIX現在被廣泛認為是亞太地區最大的Internet交換點之一。<br />\n<br />\n詳見來源截圖：<a href=\"https://businessdigest.io/post/1324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessdigest.io%2Fpost%2F1324&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7X4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=ddc11c0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessdigest.io/post/1324</a><br />\n來源：香港中文大學校友事務處專頁、Hong Kong Internet Exchange"},{"pid":"6fa1cb7e194c1ecdefbc1d48c9c896027f7f18c6","tid":1712960,"uid":64151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f58b0e7ca2fbd238639918bf4abc0792a81b623","tid":1712960,"uid":58089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"屌 仲傳緊HKIX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f9af74c6ff2e05bbc39d8eaada7f69bb42c5de","tid":1712960,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n最新：Hawley 出第二條關於中大的tweet!<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1194269562608463879?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1194269562608463879%3Fs%3D20&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7X4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=3d2f9a65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1194269562608463879%3Fs%3D20&h=dd03ffb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1194269562608463879?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n第一條<br />\n（twitter 突發）美國參議員Hawley 為警察攻入中大校園出聲啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅任務同link去 @TwitterHelpBot，admin團隊會繼續更新。"},{"pid":"825ca700fa851cb364fa63262e3c869da2d95597","tid":1712960,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:56:59.000Z","msg":"無以為報 暴大新一代革命先峰"},{"pid":"69f6a07c3766bfc0dc07fa171daca47daf2dd370","tid":1712960,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c978840ff23201b89a541c39cd57601e2995931e","tid":1712960,"uid":270489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"請廣傳！【緊急行動】香港已陷人道危機，和理非請到英領美領請願！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712624</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8819320f7ce210346ee3c3be5f3a78b11be9b4ee","tid":1712960,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f58b0e7ca2fbd238639918bf4abc0792a81b623","tid":1712960,"uid":58089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTim